Killer's eyes widen as he sees the rocket coming at him. Several seconds 
later, Killer's charred body is laying almost a mile away from the 
Cybertronian Fire, the bot in stasis lock.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
"Die, maximal!" Zeus yells, transforming into his robot mode as he dives at 
Hot Rod, swinging his sword at the Maximal.
